    <td width="50%" background="images/qeustbak.gif" tppabs="/images/qeustbak.gif" bgcolor="#000080"><p align="center"><strong><font color="#C4C4FF" size="5">Imo bang nakaplagan ug nasinati ang
    kinabuhi nga </font><font size="6" color="#C4C4FF">Napuno sa Espiritu?</font></strong></td>
    <td width="25%" bgcolor="#000080">

    </td>
